  Task for this lab:

Using the Semaphore class we need to create a program that demonstrates the Ren-dezvous pattern. 
A rendezvous occurs between two threads when thereis a point (in the code) 
that both threads must reach before either cancontinue. (A meeting point or checkpoint)
